title: Requires all retail establishments for on-premises consumption employing one or more persons as bouncers to require such persons to submit fingerprints
summary: Requires all retail establishments for on-premises consumption employing one or more persons as bouncers to require such persons to submit fingerprints.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the alcoholic beverage control law, in relation to criminal history information for persons employed as bouncers at all retail establishments for on-premises consumption and in relation to the licensure and training of bouncers
